C. Find the total sales amount for each product category.

SELECT 
    p.Category, 
    SUM(s.TotalAmount) AS CategoryTotalSales
FROM Products p
JOIN Sales s ON p.ProductID = s.ProductID
GROUP BY p.Category;

D. Identify the customers who made purchases in a speciﬁc city.

